label: Hazard

label: Fate and Transport
content: (degradation OR bioaccumulation OR sunlight OR bacteria OR breakdown OR transport[tiab])

label: Metabolism/PK/PD
content: (metabolism OR metabolite OR tissue distribution OR pharmacokinetics OR pharmacodynamics)

label: Chemical Properties
content: (logp OR solubility OR equilibrium OR solute or "partition coefficient"[tiab] OR hydrophob* OR hydrophil*)

label: Exposure
content: (exposure OR near-field OR far-field OR nhanes OR Environmental Monitoring OR Environmental Exposure OR exposome)

label: Mixtures
content: (Drug synergism[mh] OR cocarcinogenesis OR  pesticide synergists[mh] OR mixture[tiab] OR mixtures[tiab] OR Drug Antagonism[mh] OR Drug Interactions[mh] OR drug agonism)

label: Male Reproduction
content: (((Reproduction[mh] OR reproduction) AND male) OR Genitalia, male[mh] OR Genital Diseases, Male[mh] OR spermatogenesis or sperm))

label: Female Reproduction

label: GeneTox
content: (dna/drug effects OR DNA Damage OR chromosome aberrations OR genotoxicity OR "genetic toxicity" OR micronucleus  OR DNA Repair OR mutagenicity tests OR mutagens OR mutagenicity OR mutagenic or "gene mutation")

label: Clinical Trials
content: ((clinical[Title/Abstract] AND trial[Title/Abstract]) OR clinical trial[Publication Type] )

label: Embryo and embryonic development
content: (embryo OR Embryonic Structures OR fetus OR Embryonic and Fetal Development)

label: Child (infant through adolescent)

label: Dust and Exposure
content: (dust AND (exposure OR near-field OR far-field OR nhanes OR Environmental Monitoring OR Environmental Exposure OR exposome))

label: Food and Exposure
content: (food AND (exposure OR near-field OR far-field OR nhanes OR Environmental Monitoring OR Environmental Exposure OR exposome))

label: Water and Exposure
content: ((water OR groundwater OR drinking water) AND (exposure OR near-field OR far-field OR nhanes OR Environmental Monitoring OR Environmental Exposure OR exposome))
